name: numeric
definition: A numeric keypad with additional symbols available.

name: date
definition: Displays the current date with options to move forward and backward by single days. A No Date option sets the date to Jan 1 2000.

name: text
definition: Opens the device software keyboard for input

name: boolean
definition: True/false button that toggles when pressed.

name: morphometric_points
definition: morphometric points equally spaced between the proximal and distal ends, proximal end point. The original coordinate point (0,0) is located in the upper left corner of the rectangle defined by the MaximumWidth and the Maximum Heigth.

name: LAB_color
definition: CIELAB color space of fruits  measured with Chromameter (Konica Minolta)
